Text::Filter::Chain provides the possibility to chain multiple
Text::Filter objects and run them in sequence.

INSTALLATION

Text::Filter::Chain is installed like any other Perl module:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

REQUIREMENTS

Text::Filter::Chain requires that the Text::Filter module is installed.

Requires perl 5.004_04 or higher.

